Φ(ReflectivePractice) = δγ(experience|cyclical-return) ⇄ ρ(felt-sense|tacit-knowing) → [σ(surprise|disturbance)] → [λ(inquiry|problem-framing)] → [β(reframing|generative-insight)] → [κ(integration|new-understanding)] + ε | :transformative

